        - weight: 80
          module:
            rid: 107151340257149035
          output: "The Overseer is not content that our only offering is spiritual
            aid. He claims that \u201Cwords of encouragement\u201D will not grant
            his men peace of mind. Many have decided to abandon our sect. Words of
            encouragement? Do they not realize we speak for the Beholder?"
        - weight: 20
          module:
            rid: 107151340257149036
          output: Our followers find peace in our words. His Gaze is upon all, and
            even the worst shall pass. This is enough to calm them, though they remain
            visibly troubled.
